heading: Micronesia.
general-note: Here are entered works on the division of Oceania that consists of Guam, the Trust Territory of the Pacific Islands, Nauru, and the Gilbert Islands.  Works on the Federated States of Micronesia, which consists of the four administrative districts of Chuuk, Yap, Pohnpei, and Kosrae, are entered under the name heading. Micronesia (Federated States)..
